OL,3,CMan guilty of murdering prison officer
OL,4,Cin 'act of retaliation'
OL,6,FA former prison guard was shot dead in
OL,7,F"an act of retaliation" after he
OL,8,Fexposed an illicit relationship
OL,9,Fbetween a convict and a female officer.
OL,11,FLenny Scott, 33, was shot six times by
OL,12,Fgunman Elias Morgan who approached him
OL,13,Fin a hi-vis jacket outside of a gym in
OL,14,FSkelmersdale, Lancashire, on 8
OL,15,FFebruary 2024.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/14
