OL,3,CMan guilty of murdering prison officer
OL,4,Cin 'act of retaliation'
OL,6,FFrom that moment, prosecuting
OL,7,Fbarrister Alex Leach KC said, Morgan
OL,8,Ftold Lenny he would get him. "He said
OL,9,Fhe would bide his time, but that he
OL,10,Fwould get him," he added.
OL,12,FMorgan, of Edge Hill in Liverpool, was
OL,13,Ffound guilty of murdering Lenny by an
OL,14,F11-person jury, consisting of eight
OL,15,Fmen and three women.
OL,17,FHe did not react as the jury returned
OL,18,Ftheir verdict and will be sentenced on
OL,19,FTuesday 2 September at 2pm.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/14
