OL,3,CMan guilty of murdering prison officer
OL,4,Cin 'act of retaliation'
OL,6,FAnother man on trial with Morgan,
OL,7,FAnthony Cleary, 29, was cleared of
OL,8,Fboth murder and manslaughter.
OL,10,FLenny's parents pay tribute to their
OL,11,Fson
OL,13,FFollowing the verdict, Lenny's
OL,14,Fparents, Neil and Paula Scott
OL,15,Fdescribed their son as "an amazing man
OL,16,Fwho had principles".
OL,18,FThey added he was a "fantastic son and
OL,19,Ffather who was full of ideas about
OL,20,Fwhat he wanted to do in the future
OL,21,Fwith his children."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/14
