OL,6,FWhen asked who was making the threat
OL,7,Fon Lenny and his family, he said:
OL,8,F"Elias Morgan. He's described my
OL,9,Ffamily, to a T and my house. He said
OL,10,Fhe's had them (men) there just ready.
OL,12,F"It's over because I nicked him for a
OL,13,Fphone and until I drop that he said
OL,14,Fthey're staying there and they're just
OL,15,Fgoing to constantly be around my
OL,16,Fhouse. I'm in fear for my family's
OL,17,Flife, that's all."
