OL,3,CMan guilty of murdering prison officer
OL,4,Cin 'act of retaliation'
OL,6,FLenny spoke calmly to the operator as
OL,7,Fshe asked him if he had noticed anyone
OL,8,Foutside his home in the days prior to
OL,9,Fthe threat, but he said he had not. He
OL,10,Ffurther explained that the threats
OL,11,Fcame as a result of an iPhone
OL,12,F"incriminating" Morgan.
OL,14,FThe dad continued: "He said he's got
OL,15,Flads everywhere. He's described my
OL,16,Fvehicle and he's described my house
OL,17,Fand what my girlfriend and twin boys
OL,18,Flook like."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/14
