OL,3,CMan guilty of murdering prison officer
OL,4,Cin 'act of retaliation'
OL,6,FSpeaking after the trial, Paula said:
OL,7,F"Once he got those threats...he was
OL,8,Freally scared for himself and his
OL,9,Ffamily. Personally he could deal with
OL,10,Fit but it was different once you
OL,11,Fbrought his children and his partner
OL,12,Finto it."
OL,14,FThe jury was also shown footage of the
OL,15,Fmoment Lenny was ambushed and shot
OL,16,Foutside a gym in Skelmersdale.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/14
