OL,4,Cin 'act of retaliation'
OL,6,FThe footage showed gunman Morgan
OL,7,Fwaiting in the car park before
OL,8,Fapproaching the prison guard and
OL,9,Fdischarging a number of shots before
OL,10,Ffleeing from the scene.
OL,12,FThe prosecution told the jury that on
OL,13,F4 January 2024 Morgan carried out a
OL,14,F"day of reconnaissance, a day of
OL,15,Fplanning, for the murder that was to
OL,16,Ffollow".
