OL,6,FThe jury heard he visited three
OL,7,Flocations with an "obvious connection
OL,8,Fto Lenny Scott", including his home
OL,9,Faddress, a gym he formerly frequented
OL,10,Fin Speke, Liverpool, and the Peel
OL,11,FHouse gym where he was later shot.
OL,13,FAs part of the planning, a van had
OL,14,Fbeen parked at the end of a cul de
OL,15,Fsac, a short distance away from the
OL,16,Fgym.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/14
