OL,3,CMan guilty of murdering prison officer
OL,4,Cin 'act of retaliation'
OL,6,FMorgan travelled from Liverpool to
OL,7,FSkelmersdale on the day of the murder,
OL,8,Fin a Mercedes vehicle registered to
OL,9,Fhis mother, leaving it a short
OL,10,Fdistance from where the van was.
OL,12,FFollowing the murder, Morgan rode an
OL,13,Felectric motorbike along footpaths and
OL,14,Facross fields, to avoid detection,
OL,15,Floading it into the van that had been
OL,16,Fleft in there day before.
OL,18,FLenny's parents said the family are
OL,19,Fnow trying to "find a new normal"
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/14
