OL,4,Cin 'act of retaliation'
OL,6,FLenny's dad Neil said following the
OL,7,Fconclusion of the trial the family
OL,8,Fwould try to "find a new normal"
OL,9,Fwithout Lenny.
OL,11,FPaula added:" It will be so hard but
OL,12,Fwe can't let them destroy all our
OL,13,Flives. We still have to carry on for
OL,14,Fthe children's sake - they still have
OL,15,Fto have a life.
OL,17,F"They'll remember him, we'll never let
OL,18,Fthem forget him but I think we just
OL,19,Fneed to move on from from this, but
OL,20,Fwe'll never move on from Lenny."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/14
