OL,3,CMan guilty of murdering prison officer
OL,4,Cin 'act of retaliation'
OL,6,FWendy Logan, Deputy Head of CPS North
OL,7,FWest's Complex Casework Unit, said
OL,8,FMorgan was driven by "revenge and
OL,9,Fbelieving he was above the law".
OL,11,F"Lenny Scott was a devoted father who
OL,12,Fhad bravely upheld his duty when
OL,13,Fworking as a prison officer, by
OL,14,Freporting an illicit phone he found in
OL,15,FElias Morgan's cell in 2020," she said.
OL,17,F"He did so in the face of attempts at
OL,18,Fbribery and also threats and
OL,19,Fintimidation by Morgan ` and his
OL,20,Fcommitment to public service will not
OL,21,Fbe forgotten.
