OL,6,F"Morgan ` driven by revenge and
OL,7,Fbelieving he was above the law `
OL,8,Fcarried out a cold-blooded murder.
OL,10,F"We were determined to deliver justice
OL,11,Fand see Morgan brought to book for his
OL,12,Fevil crime ` and our case set out in
OL,13,Fclear terms how he planned and carried
OL,14,Fout his callous act.
OL,16,F"Our thoughts remain with Lenny's
OL,17,Ffamily ` particularly his three young
OL,18,Fchildren ` and all those who cared for
OL,19,Fhim, as they deal with his loss."
